The paper discusses the evaluation of sentence embeddings, which is a subfield of natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses deep learning models, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses the weaknesses of model evaluation, which is a topic in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also mentions normalization and correlations, which are topics in cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), respectively.
